 Since the launch of Caldert Griffon in March 2017, demand for the lightweight welder has been impressive so far and continues to fill the order book. A combination of Caldervale Technology’s reliable electronics and the weight reduction to 12kg a unit has captured the plumbers / civils markets install HDPE pipe sizes up to 200mm. The Calder Griffon is full of features to help installers productivity and capture weld data. Contact our sales team to arrange your demonstration.    